

=Bio=

"Currently, I am a student of M.Sc. in Economics, Politics, and Philosophy at Hamburg University in Germany. Before that I have been studying Economics in Berlin, Utrecht, and Barcelona.

My main interests are the Commons, with a focus on its environmental and social implications as well as its relation to topics such as economic growth and socio-environmental sustainability. 

Other than that I have worked in the field of development cooperation and been part of different social movements, I travel a lot and do rock-climbing."

